body_html: I faced this error when I tried to use Go load a savedmodel I trained with Python. And I found the library other language(c, c++, go etc) use is built by the rule in BUILD files. And I addethat two lines in file and succeed. So I think if you face a error like "Op type not registered XXX", you can check whether it was built into the library you use.
